QuestData.Title: Amani Invasion
QuestData.Description: Though you don't understand the language in these battle plans, you clearly make out a map marking the positions of the Farstrider Retreat and Fairbreeze Village.$B$BYou'd best let Lieutenant Dawnrunner at the Farstrider Retreat know about this.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Amani Invasion Plans to Lieutenant Dawnrunner at Farstrider Retreat.
QuestData.CompletionText: What do you want to show me?
QuestData.RewardText: The trolls have been keeping us pinned here while planning an attack on Fairbreeze Village. We were not expecting this at all.
